description: Lists the specified export tasks. You can list all your export tasks or filter the results based on task ID or task status.

nested_items.name: taskId
nested_items.description: The ID of the export task.

nested_items.name: taskName
nested_items.description: The name of the export task.

nested_items.name: logGroupName
nested_items.description: The name of the log group from which logs data was exported.

nested_items.name: from
nested_items.description: The start time, expressed as the number of milliseconds after Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC. Events with a timestamp before this time are not exported.

nested_items.name: to
nested_items.description: The end time, expressed as the number of milliseconds after Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC. Events with a timestamp later than this time are not exported.

nested_items.name: destination
nested_items.description: The name of the S3 bucket to which the log data was exported.

nested_items.name: destinationPrefix
nested_items.description: The prefix that was used as the start of Amazon S3 key for every object exported.

nested_items.name: code
nested_items.description: The status code of the export task.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The status message related to the status code.

nested_items.name: executionInfo
nested_items.description: Execution information about the export task.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The creation time of the export task, expressed as the number of milliseconds after Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC.

nested_items.name: completionTime
nested_items.description: The completion time of the export task, expressed as the number of milliseconds after Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of items to return. The token expires after 24 hours.
